data.description: Mountain Views - Fruit Trees - Vegetable Garden - Herb Garden - Mature shade trees. Come see this well maintained home 3 bedroom, 2 bath located in the heart of a well established neighborhood without HOA fees. Situated across the street from a golf course and pond. Large four-seasons room equipped with a pellet stove offers a comfortable place to gather with stunning mountain views. The front porch is enclosed and has a cozy swing that conveys with the house and is the perfect setting for morning coffee or afternoon relaxation. Large 1/2 acre lot boasts RV parking with electrical, sewer & water hook ups & porch. The back yard is fully fenced with a drive-through gate, shed & rich garden area. All new appliances in kitchen, newer water heater, new washer & dryer and garage fridge convey. Home warranty is in place and transferable to new owner. Electric panel has all new breakers installed and the AC unit was recently maintained. Inside has recently been painted.
